detailedDescription.articleBody: The Ministry of Road Transport and Highways is a ministry of the Government of India, that is the apex body for formulation and administration of the rules, regulations and laws relating to road transport, transport research and in also to increase the mobility and efficiency of the road transport system in India.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Pittsburgh is a city in the state of Pennsylvania in the United States, and is the county seat of Allegheny County.
